name: The Mountains
description:
This is what the minds eye sees, when the words “Blue Mountains” are spoken. A childhood of mist soaked mountain ranges. Travelling from Sydney, you see the blue on the horizon as eucalyptus oils rise in the air. Sun rises over my mountains and it is beauty you’ve never felt before.

This artwork is an animated photograph of handmade wool, viscose and silk felt, made using wet felting methods. Rose Jackson, 2021
